<br>
If PoTallonar suddenly decides it's vitally important to his RP that Tallonar cheats on Didi, I'm fine with that (as a player) but I would certainly expect that he would warn me the player <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">in advance</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, seeing as Didi's 50 year marriage would be about to end chaotically and I'd drastically have to change her comfortable little family story and her behaviour quite significantly.  Just common courtesy and respect for another player.<br>
